## Suggested Study Order

1. Basics
   - HTTP fundamentals
   - REST APIs
   - JSON structure

2. Client Setup
   - Retrofit basics
   - OkHttp configuration
   - Interceptors

3. Data Handling
   - Gson serialization
   - Converter factories
   - Error handling

4. Advanced Features
   - Logging strategies
   - Lazy initialization
   - Builder patterns

